title Creating a new Note (SPA)

browser->server: HTTP POST https://fullstack-exampleapp.herokuapp.com/new_note_spa

note over server:
Server adds new note to
`notes` object by extracting
data from request body, then
saves `notes` object to data.json
end note

server-->browser: status 201 Created

note over browser:
browser executes event handler that
was attached to the submit event
of the form, adding the new note to the ul
end note
